#8002
Near a Large Building~
   You are standing on the path that runs around the Wayhouse
to the west.  A window spills light onto the trees that block
out all available light overhead.  You hear general merryment
and alcoholism from inside, and wonder if being inside would 
be more fun than walking around outside...
