Near a Large Building~
   You are south-west of the main structure of the Wayhouse. 
A lone rain barrel catches run-off from the roof eaves by the
corner of the building, and you spy a small white fence 
cordoning off an herb garden nearby.  The path around the 
building leads to the north and east.
