#8004
Outside the Wayhouse~
   You are standing just south of Werith's Wayhouse, right 
where the kitchen entrance is.  A well trodden path leads 
east, towards a small shack that is unmistakeably an outhouse.
You hear the unmistakeable sound of clanging pots and pans 
from the inside, the warning of an upcoming meal.  The path 
around the building here runs east, and west.
