Just Outside the Stable~
   The stable of the Wayhouse is just south of you, its 
wooden doors spread open and inviting.  Inside you can hear 
the snorting of horses, and the occasional hoof scraping 
against the ground.  The path leads to the west, towards the 
Wayhouse.
