   You are standing inside the dusty confines of the stable. 
Stalls line the aisle, some with horses, some empty.  A pail 
filled with water and a stack of grain are heaped up against 
the interior wall, dimly illuminated by a lantern hanging 
from a rafter.  Seems rather quiet in here...
