#8013
Main Room~
   The bar runs south here all along the western wall.   A 
few smaller tables here are set up with various board games, 
ready to play.  There's also a shelf along the wall, lined 
with a few popular books; light reading all of them.  The 
patrons here seem to be a bit quieter than the rowdy bunch 
in the rest of the building.
~
