#8014
Main Room~
   A window here offers a view outside, where it doesn't seem
near as social as it is inside.   Tables filled with laughing
customers eat and drink and generally be merry, not caring 
what the weather is like, and probably not even knowing.  
There's a general sense of joy in the room; the joy of still 
being alive in such a dangerous world as this one.  For a 
moment, you feel like joining them...
~
