#8015
Main Room~
   You stand just inside the Main Room of Werith's Wayhouse. 
The whole place stretches out all around you, a 
conglomeration of people, food, and alcohol.  The sheer 
chatter and roar of conversation makes your ears hurt a 
little, and then you suddenly notice you're smiling.  Yes, 
this place might do for awhile...
