#8016
Main Room~
   The giant fireplace here sends a great amount of heat 
throughout the room.  The sheer massiveness of the stone 
edifice and the literal bonfire inside makes you give the 
area a clear way.  A few of the older and less human 
residents of the inn seem to be enjoying these tables, 
however.
