#8017
Main Room~
   Several dart boards line the wall to the south, and darts 
are scattered all about on the tables and stuck in the wall. 
The people coming up and down the stairs to the east 
carefully walk by the wall to avoid being pin-cushioned 
involuntarily, and you think it would be a good idea to do 
the same.
