#8018
Main Room~
   The tables seem to thin out around here, to give room for 
the traffic going in and out of the kitchen through the 
archway to the south.  Waiters and waitresses march in and 
out with empty plates and sumptuous platters, hardly stopping
to breathe in their business.  You hear the distant clank of 
a pot banging against something -- the chefs are busy too it 
seems.   Your stomach growls...are you hungry at all?
