Main Room~
   The wooden bar runs along the length of the western wall, 
just in front of the many shelves of different colored 
alcohol in different shaped bottles.  You espy drunkards and 
waitresses, adventurers and farmers althroughout the building
from this vantage point, and guess that this establishment is
turning a pretty penny in profits.  Nice.
