#8023
Kitchen~
   This is the main entranceway of the kitchen.  Two archways
serve as an entry and exit point from the main room of the 
wayhouse, one north, one west.  The kitchen is a room roughly
thirty feet by thirty feet, extending from the south and east
from here.  You see many pots on the stove bubbling away and 
hear the whistle of a kettle somewhere off to the left...
business must be good.
