Kitchen~
   You are standing in a more quiet area of the kitchen, 
where various supplies of flour, grain and meats are kept.  
The kitchen extends south and west from here; that's where 
the main clutter seems to be.  A steady thump-thump-thump 
from the north wall reminds you that the main room is where 
are the fun and action seems to be...
