#8027
Main Room~
   This is a quiet, darkened corner -- it appears someone 
has put out the lantern here on purpose.  You feel a chill, 
probably due to your distance from the fire, and rub your 
arms absently.  There's a table set near the corner, a single
chair behind it in the shadowy of shadows.  You get the 
cliche'd feeling someone in robes should be sitting there.
