#8029
Stairwell~
   Some sturdy wooden stairs lead up to the second floor of 
the wayhouse, where there are a few rooms for rent.  A lonely
lantern lights the way up, glinting off the polished 
handrail.  An arch to the east opens up into the main room...
where the noise informs you that the revelry hasn't stopped 
yet.
