#8030
Stairwell~
   A stairwell here leads back down to the first floor and 
the main room  of the wayhouse.  A hallway leads east along 
the second floor here, lined with doors to private bedrooms. 
The floors, stairs, and walls are all made with sturdy oak 
in contrast of the heavy stone of the exterior walls.  A 
light at the top of the stairs throws illumination down the 
hall.
